  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>                                    </i>Elysium – The Truths Hidden in the Darkness</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/991714862e8545cc828cf24d84279474.poster.avif?t=1740245641\" width=640 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/991714862e8545cc828cf24d84279474.webm?t=1740245641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/991714862e8545cc828cf24d84279474.mp4?t=1740245641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sebastian lived his life as an ordinary janitor. Every day, as he wandered through the cold walls of the nursing home, questions about his past lingered in his mind. But that night, everything changed. Strange noises, missing patients, and a doctor shrouded in mystery… Elysium Nursing Home was far from ordinary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When Sebastian found himself trapped in an incomprehensible nightmare, he realized there was no turning back. In a place where unimaginable experiments took place, people vanished without a trace, and the line between reality and hallucination blurred, he had to follow the traces of the past to survive. But as he ventured deeper into the nursing home’s dark corridors, he began to question his own sanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Elysium</strong> invites you into a world dominated by psychological tension, uncertainty, and fear. Players will have to navigate the growing doubts within Sebastian’s mind. Who can you trust? Which memories are real? And most importantly… how will you escape?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/f56e0b72951dac5060ba0d9cdb381645.poster.avif?t=1740245641\" width=640 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/f56e0b72951dac5060ba0d9cdb381645.webm?t=1740245641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/f56e0b72951dac5060ba0d9cdb381645.mp4?t=1740245641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Story:</strong> Experience the despair of a man confronting his own past.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric Horror:</strong> Walk through dark corridors filled with a deep sense of loneliness and uncertainty.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mind Games:</strong> Explore the thin line between reality and delusion, and uncover the terrifying truth that awaits you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Graphic Style:</strong> Immerse yourself in an unforgettable nightmare with low-polygon visuals inspired by the aesthetics of 90s games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzle and Exploration Mechanics:</strong> Gather clues from your surroundings to uncover the horrifying truth behind the nursing home.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this mind-bending mystery, the most important question is: <strong>Do you really want to escape?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/2036519daed075e29c552b36ae0d5af2.poster.avif?t=1740245641\" width=640 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/2036519daed075e29c552b36ae0d5af2.webm?t=1740245641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/2036519daed075e29c552b36ae0d5af2.mp4?t=1740245641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FPS Horror Experience:</strong> Navigate through the darkness, confronting your fears with every step. Fear will follow you at every turn.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intense Psychological Horror:</strong> In the eerie halls of the asylum, you must stay alert at all times.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rich Story and Exploration:</strong> Examine your surroundings carefully to uncover mysterious events and hidden truths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzles and Thought-Provoking Tasks:</strong> Piece together clues to reveal the horrifying reality behind the asylum.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Untrustworthy Characters:</strong> Can you truly trust Dr. Malverick, or is he a part of a twisted game leading you toward madness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/a479d75984da717f7e7782c97e5c3708.poster.avif?t=1740245641\" width=640 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/a479d75984da717f7e7782c97e5c3708.webm?t=1740245641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/a479d75984da717f7e7782c97e5c3708.mp4?t=1740245641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/a9e20c5e98f73f220241f7da03a19037.poster.avif?t=1740245641\" width=640 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/a9e20c5e98f73f220241f7da03a19037.webm?t=1740245641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414470/extras/a9e20c5e98f73f220241f7da03a19037.mp4?t=1740245641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
